- **Framework:** [Next.js](mdc:https:/nextjs.org) (`next`)
- **Language:** [TypeScript](mdc:https:/www.typescriptlang.org) (`typescript`, `tsconfig.json`)
- **Styling:** [Tailwind CSS](mdc:https:/tailwindcss.com) (`tailwind.config.js`, `css/`)
- **Content Management:** [Contentlayer](mdc:https:/contentlayer.dev) (`contentlayer.config.ts`, `next-contentlayer2`)
- **Linting/Formatting:** [ESLint](mdc:https:/eslint.org) (`.eslintrc.js`), [Prettier](mdc:https:/prettier.io) (`prettier.config.js`)
- **Package Manager:** [pnpm](mdc:https:/pnpm.io) (`pnpm-lock.yaml`)
